                     <interp inst="t18410705-1901-verdict-1" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18410705-1901-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">GUILTY</hi> of Larceny only.</rs> Aged 18.</p>
